| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-1278 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 7d53f4f8-8e6c-5b31-ae1b-c425754aaa38"
